#: ../../source/deploy/server/kubernetes/deploy-k8s-aks.rst:9
msgid ""
"**An AKS cluster**: with the `Application Gateway Ingress Controller "
"(AGIC) add-on <https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/application-"
"gateway/tutorial-ingress-controller-add-on-new>`_ enabled or another "
"Ingress controller deployed."
